I'm going then.

00:15:44.640 --> 00:15:45.440
Safety first.

00:15:48.040 --> 00:15:49.040
You stay safe too.

00:15:51.560 --> 00:15:52.620
Protect yourself.

00:15:55.200 --> 00:15:55.800
Aunt Rong!

00:15:56.800 --> 00:15:57.400
Don't run!

00:15:58.920 --> 00:16:00.520
Turn back before it's too late!

00:16:00.520 --> 00:16:01.050
Qiu Chen!

00:16:02.400 --> 00:16:03.400
I have ALS.

00:16:03.400 --> 00:16:04.930
I don't have much time left.

00:16:05.880 --> 00:16:08.120
I just want to find a quiet place to die.

00:16:08.120 --> 00:16:09.250
Can't I even do that?

00:16:09.920 --> 00:16:11.520
Why are you still lying to me?

00:16:12.480 --> 00:16:12.920
First,

00:16:14.600 --> 00:16:15.880
you don't have ALS.

00:16:16.560 --> 00:16:19.490
You forged all those medical records and diagnoses.

00:16:19.680 --> 00:16:20.140
Second,

00:16:20.800 --> 00:16:22.600
you aren't going to die quietly.

00:16:22.920 --> 00:16:26.050
You want to go abroad to continue your cleaner business.

00:16:26.360 --> 00:16:29.020
You've already obtained foreign citizenship.

00:16:29.240 --> 00:16:31.040
Once you escape to the high seas,

00:16:31.680 --> 00:16:33.940
it will be much harder for us to catch you.

00:16:34.640 --> 00:16:35.400
I can tell you

00:16:36.480 --> 00:16:37.680
that all the ports right now

00:16:37.680 --> 00:16:39.680
have been locked down by the police.

00:16:40.080 --> 00:16:41.080
You can't escape.

00:16:41.480 --> 00:16:42.080
Is that so?

00:16:43.800 --> 00:16:45.560
Then if I take you as a hostage,

00:16:46.800 --> 00:16:48.480
I can force them to clear a path, right?